WEBVTT

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 13=

00:00:12.839 --> 00:00:13.439
Hua.

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:16.160
Whatever you want to do,

00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:18.280
whatever you want me to do,

00:00:19.679 --> 00:00:22.480
I'm willing to stay with you
and wait for you.

00:00:49.799 --> 00:00:51.719
Hua, it's Yun.

00:00:54.759 --> 00:00:55.719
Yun is back.

00:00:56.159 --> 00:00:57.439
He won't hurt you again.

00:00:58.240 --> 00:00:59.679
Hua.

00:01:00.080 --> 00:01:00.600
It's me, Yun.

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:02.159
Yun is here, don't be afraid.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:03.280
Hua.

00:01:10.439 --> 00:01:11.439
Yun is here.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:12.830
Don't be afraid.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:26.640
It's alright.

00:01:28.040 --> 00:01:28.879
No rush.

00:01:30.359 --> 00:01:31.439
We'll take it slow.

00:01:55.519 --> 00:01:56.799
Now you've been exiled,

00:01:57.079 --> 00:01:59.959
how can a woman like me survive?

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:02.879
Qing Yan.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.319
You wretched woman!

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:05.879
Behave!

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.560
Officer!

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.319
Madam, General instructed

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:10.759
that you would be here

00:02:10.919 --> 00:02:12.080
to see this man off,

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:14.719
and told me to guard carefully,

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:16.120
not to let Madam get hurt.

00:02:19.199 --> 00:02:20.039
Don't worry, Madam.

00:02:20.199 --> 00:02:21.319
I'll take good care of him

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.800
on the road.

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:25.680
You think if I'm gone,

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.319
You'll have good days?

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:29.479
Behind the Xiao family

00:02:30.260 --> 00:02:31.770
are people you can't afford to offend!

00:02:32.919 --> 00:02:35.240
Everything I suffer today

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:38.479
will one day come back to you.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:39.960
Still showing off?

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:41.560
Officer, don't hit him!

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:42.840
What you suffer today

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:44.520
is retribution for your own evil.

00:02:44.719 --> 00:02:46.159
How can that be blamed on our lady?

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:46.800
Enough.

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.919
Xiao Lian, he's already defeated.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:51.719
We don't need to waste words.

00:02:51.919 --> 00:02:52.560
Let's go.

00:02:53.159 --> 00:02:53.919
Madam, take care.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.199
Qing Yan!

00:02:55.639 --> 00:02:56.800
Go, hurry up!

00:02:57.879 --> 00:02:59.240
You'll face retribution!

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:00.680
Madam.

00:03:00.919 --> 00:03:03.120
Please spare our master.

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:04.960
How can you say that?

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.680
That old man did evil himself,

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:08.840
the court examined him and exiled him.

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.719
How is it our lady's fault?

00:03:11.479 --> 00:03:12.319
I know

00:03:12.719 --> 00:03:14.560
I can't speak well, I'm clumsy.

00:03:15.639 --> 00:03:16.400
But

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.680
if Madam could help a little.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:20.840
Back when you two

00:03:21.039 --> 00:03:22.719
bullied Xiao Lian and the others,

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:24.840
did you ever think of them?

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:27.240
I see you

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:29.280
as just a jackal by the tiger's side,

00:03:29.479 --> 00:03:30.719
so I won't argue with you.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:33.159
Xiao Lian, let's go.

00:03:47.900 --> 00:03:50.820
(Mochun Brothel)

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.199
Thank you

00:03:59.159 --> 00:03:59.960
for today.

00:04:02.479 --> 00:04:03.680
We are husband and wife,

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:05.120
no need for thanks.

00:04:23.439 --> 00:04:25.079
Why did you bring me here?

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:29.839
You live in the Xiao Residence,
that place is full of wolves and tigers.

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.120
I worry.

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:34.959
I've bought Mochun Brothel.

00:04:35.399 --> 00:04:36.319
From now on,

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:37.879
it belongs to you.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.759
But Mochun Brothel

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:50.759
is a place that sells women's looks.

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:53.480
Yun.

00:04:55.879 --> 00:04:57.040
You know me...

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.759
Those fallen here
are all pitiful people.

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:06.319
Yun.

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:09.560
I don't want to profit from this.

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.720
What about the people here?

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:14.519
If you don't want to see them,

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:16.879
give them some money and send them off.

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:19.519
If you worry they have no place to go,

00:05:20.079 --> 00:05:21.480
and want them to stay,

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:22.680
whether to work

00:05:22.759 --> 00:05:23.839
and run proper business

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:26.319
or just have shelter here,

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:27.920
it's all up to you.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:37.959
I only hope

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:39.959
you can sleep peacefully.

00:05:41.199 --> 00:05:43.959
No longer fearing to be framed.

00:06:05.439 --> 00:06:06.759
With you by my side,

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.680
I can already sleep peacefully.

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:14.680
Someone else wants to see you
outside the door.

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:17.000
Come with me.

00:06:27.879 --> 00:06:28.519
These

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:31.519
are all people once bullied
by the Zhang couple.

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:34.680
Now they all wish to thank you.

00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:37.030
- Thank you, Madam.
- Thank you, Madam.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.500
- Madam, you are so kind.
- Madam, you are so kind.

00:06:38.519 --> 00:06:39.000
Thank you.

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:39.839
No need to thank me.

00:06:40.519 --> 00:06:42.680
This is the punishment
the Zhang couple deserved.

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:44.399
You may go back now.

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:46.420
- Thank you, Madam.
- Thank you, Madam.

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:48.180
- Madam, you are so kind.
- Madam, you are so kind.

00:06:48.199 --> 00:06:50.399
- Thank you.
- Many thanks.

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:52.120
Now,

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:53.959
only Grand Madam Xiao

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:56.140
has not received the punishment
she deserves.

00:06:57.959 --> 00:06:58.839
You're so clever,

00:06:59.279 --> 00:07:00.439
how could she escape?

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:03.879
But Yun,

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:05.600
I'm a little tired

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.040
of this life of schemes.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.160
Why don't we just leave?

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:12.439
The mountains are high, the seas wide,
there'll always be a place for us.

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.319
What do you think?

00:07:13.439 --> 00:07:14.040
Of course.

00:07:14.670 --> 00:07:16.120
The sky is vast, the seas boundless.

00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:17.800
As long as I'm with you,

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:19.240
anywhere is fine.

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:23.839
General.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.920
Your resignation was rejected.

00:07:32.879 --> 00:07:33.560
Why?

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.160
Speak.

00:07:38.839 --> 00:07:39.800
By the Emperor's decree,

00:07:39.820 --> 00:07:41.800
the Empress Dowager
will bring Princess Zhaoping

00:07:41.879 --> 00:07:44.490
to stay at the Xiao Residence
to thank the General for saving her.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:46.319
So the resignation is denied.

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.319
General, it seems

00:07:48.319 --> 00:07:50.040
you've won the princess's heart.

00:07:50.279 --> 00:07:51.120
Nonsense.

00:07:52.519 --> 00:07:53.680
There's no such heart.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:55.879
We'll leave right now.

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:57.079
The world is vast,

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.240
anywhere will do.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:01.439
Yun.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.480
You can walk away,

00:08:03.839 --> 00:08:05.839
but your soldiers will suffer.

00:08:08.600 --> 00:08:10.040
Besides, didn't you say

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.399
I'm clever?

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:13.240
Since I'm so clever,

00:08:13.519 --> 00:08:14.360
how could I ever

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:16.639
hand over the man I love
to someone else?

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:18.759
Not even to a princess.

00:08:24.199 --> 00:08:25.279
After the Flower Festival,

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:28.160
the Empress Dowager
and the princess will visit our home.

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:30.639
What I mean is,

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:33.320
let Xiao Ye be in charge
of receiving them.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.440
He's but a commoner,

00:08:35.879 --> 00:08:37.679
he must earn an official title.

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.879
This is the perfect chance.

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:42.519
If Qing Yan has no objection,

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:44.840
then hand over the steward's token.

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:49.039
With just a few words from Grand Madam,

00:08:49.399 --> 00:08:50.679
all the household money

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:52.159
ends up in his hands.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:53.759
I'd say,

00:08:53.919 --> 00:08:55.720
Second Master Xiao
may lack other skills,

00:08:55.879 --> 00:08:57.720
but he has plenty of tricks.

00:08:58.000 --> 00:09:00.279
Enough to slice into a whole plate

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:02.080
and drink a few cups of wine.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.240
When the garden isn't even finished,

00:09:04.279 --> 00:09:05.679
he'll have gambled the money away.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:06.519
Qing Yan.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:08.519
Don't look down on me.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:09.960
I'll prove to you

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.559
I too can handle this.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.919
Fine, then tell me.

00:09:15.399 --> 00:09:18.200
How much is a candle outside?

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:21.120
Candle?

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:24.840
I suppose... Ten copper coins each.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.120
Grand Madam.

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:29.519
If you truly

00:09:29.840 --> 00:09:31.600
feel safe giving him
the household money,

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.639
then let him take charge.

00:09:33.799 --> 00:09:35.759
When the Empress Dowager
and princess arrive,

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:38.120
and use our heads as balls to kick,

00:09:39.080 --> 00:09:40.399
it'll count as loyalty.

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:43.759
Qing Yan.

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:45.590
This matter of receiving them

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:47.440
will still fall to you.

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:55.320
I'll handle

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:57.279
the princess.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:09:59.639
Why? What did I say wrong?

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:03.399
How much does a candle really cost?

00:10:11.919 --> 00:10:12.600
Mother.

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:16.519
I… I just missed a zero, didn't I?

00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:18.039
Now all that easy money

00:10:18.159 --> 00:10:19.679
has gone straight into her mouth.

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:22.679
Princess Zhaoping

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:25.000
is not someone easy to deal with.

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:26.600
For sleep, she wants a jade bed.

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:28.120
For meals, she wants gold-inlaid bowls.

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.039
You think she's easy to serve?

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:33.240
Normally, if something goes wrong,

00:10:33.559 --> 00:10:35.720
it's just a beating
and losing some silver.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:37.840
But if this goes wrong,

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:40.840
then our heads will truly roll.

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:44.440
So you mean,

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.039
today you deliberately provoked her

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:48.519
to make her take on this job?

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:53.080
Don't worry, if she does it well,

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:55.480
it'll be the glory of Xiao family.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.720
Naturally, I'll make sure you benefit.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.679
If she does it poorly,

00:11:00.679 --> 00:11:02.480
then it's her crime,

00:11:02.759 --> 00:11:04.320
and has nothing to do with us.

00:11:07.220 --> 00:11:09.620
(Sure to die)

00:11:15.530 --> 00:11:17.360
The Empress Dowager
and Princess are carefree,

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.279
patting their bottoms
and coming whenever.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.159
But us?

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:22.399
Poor folk at the market, no people,

00:11:22.399 --> 00:11:23.320
(Silk, brocade, Shu brocade)
no money either.

00:11:23.380 --> 00:11:24.799
How are we supposed to receive them?

00:11:25.020 --> 00:11:27.370
I think the Grand Madam
is just making things hard for you.

00:11:27.380 --> 00:11:28.400
Why don't you go tomorrow

00:11:28.410 --> 00:11:29.860
and tell them to figure it
out themselves?

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:30.879
Let's not bother.

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:31.960
That won't do.

00:11:32.279 --> 00:11:33.519
We already agreed,

00:11:33.519 --> 00:11:34.879
how can we go back on our word?

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:36.080
Besides,

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:38.720
only if we befriend
the Empress Dowager and Princess,

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:40.280
will we have the chance to avenge

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:41.159
Xiao Lian

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:43.480
and those other wronged women.

00:11:43.679 --> 00:11:45.679
I must receive them properly.

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:50.639
But they want so many things,

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:52.960
where are you supposed to get them?

00:11:56.279 --> 00:11:57.080
I don't know.

00:11:57.759 --> 00:11:58.360
But,

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:00.679
someone does.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:21.400
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:12:21.400 --> 00:12:24.600
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:28.600
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:32.680
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:37.440
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:12:38.040 --> 00:12:40.480
♪When we first met♪

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:48.200
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:53.080
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:57.160
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:12:57.840 --> 00:13:01.480
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:05.080
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:13:05.080 --> 00:13:08.960
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:13.280
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:17.480
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:23.280
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪